summary: Cable discusses truck traffic and tube-like objects seen entering Torrens base in Cuba between October 9 and November 7, 1963. Source reports trucks covered with canvas traveling towards Torrens, the former reformatory on the Wajay Highway southwest of Habana. Tube-like objects protruding from trucks observed on October 11.
title: TRUCK TRAFFIC AND TUBE-LIKE OBJECTS SEEN ENTERING TORRENS BASE
